    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label" style="color:var(--dusty-coral);">Virtual Tour</div>
      <h2>See The Space Before You Visit</h2>
      <p>A guided walkthrough with Hugo, our General Manager - room by room, so you can get a real feel for the venue before deciding whether to book a discovery call.</p>
      <div class="video-placeholder">
